<p><b>RACIAL JUSTICE DIALOGUES</b>. Today’s scriptures
remind us that God brings peace, “for now his greatness
shall reach to the ends of the earth.” How do we join in
the work to bring peace and healing? Join us for this
five-week series for parishioners who desire to more
deeply explore questions at the intersection of faith and
racial justice. Mondays, January 21–February 25.
Registration required by January 15 at 
<a target="_bulletin" href="http://www.stjames-cathedral.org/immigrant">http://www.stjames-cathedral.org/immigrant</a>. 
<i>Information</i>,
<a href="mailto:ckoehler@stjames-cathedral.orgckoehler@stjames-cathedral.org?subject=Racial Justice Dialogs">Christopher Koehler</a>, 206-382-4511.</p>
<p><b>DETENTION LOTTERY</b>. Join us for an immersive theatre
