<a href="mailto:ckoehler@stjames-cathedral.org?subject=Detention Lottery">Christopher Koehler</a>, 206-382-4511.</p>
<p><b>THE ST. JAMES WINTER SHELTER</b> can welcome up to
266 individuals in one month. Our hospitality provides
